OL,3,CCumbrian MP has Labour whip restored
OL,4,Cafter rebelling against 'family farm
OL,5,Ctax'
OL,7,FA Cumbrian MP has had the Labour whip
OL,8,Frestored after rebelling against
OL,9,F'family farm tax'.
OL,11,FMarkus Campbell-Savours, who
OL,12,Frepresents Penrith and Solway, has
OL,13,Fbeen reinstated as a Labour MP after
OL,14,Fhe was suspended in December for
OL,15,Fvoting against the government's plans
OL,16,Fto impose inheritance tax on farms.
OL,18,FThe vote took place before the policy
OL,19,Fwas amended.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
