CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1773144741
OL,3,CCumbrian MP has Labour whip restored
OL,4,Cafter rebelling against 'family farm
OL,5,Ctax'
OL,7,FFollowing months of protests, the
OL,8,Fgovernment later watered down plans to
OL,9,Fraise inheritance tax for farmers by
OL,10,Fincreasing the threshold for full
OL,11,Frelief from #1 million to #2.5 million.
OL,13,FMarkus Campbell-Savours MP said that
OL,14,Fis was "about time" the whip was
OL,15,Frestored.
OL,17,F"Farmers were told the Government
OL,18,Fwouldn't introduce inheritance tax on
OL,19,Ffarms and I objected to them breaking
OL,20,Fthis promise.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1773144741
OL,3,CCumbrian MP has Labour whip restored
OL,4,Cafter rebelling against 'family farm
OL,5,Ctax'
OL,7,F"Whilst I am relieved to have the
OL,8,FLabour whip back, I am more relieved
OL,9,Fthe Government delivered a major U-
OL,10,Fturn before Christmas. One I know will
OL,11,Fmake a significant difference to many
OL,12,Ffarming families in Cumbria.
OL,14,F"Having the whip removed is not a
OL,15,Fpleasant experience and whilst I have
OL,16,Fno desire to make a habit of it, I
OL,17,Fwill always do what I can to look
OL,18,Fafter our people in Cumbria."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUzD@]O]
