PN,35604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1773144741
OL,3,CCumbrian MP has Labour whip restored
OL,4,Cafter rebelling against 'family farm
OL,5,Ctax'
OL,7,FCampbell-Savours was the only Labour
OL,8,FMP to object the vote before
OL,9,FChristmas, though a number of others
OL,10,Fraised concerns and abstained.
OL,12,FThe vote related to the Budget, making
OL,13,Fhis rebellion more serious.
OL,15,FDuring a debate in the House of
OL,16,FCommons at the time, Mr Campbell-
OL,17,FSavours said there are 1,665 farms in
OL,18,Fhis constituency, and the policy would
OL,19,Fleave many farmers "devastated at the
OL,20,Fimpact on their family farms."
OL,26,@{D@TOU|D@^O]
